{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/docs/get-started/install","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"fields":{"slug":"/docs/get-started/install"},"id":"ed2c83a2-5eff-50dc-a12b-360f3488eec5","html":"<h2 id=\"准备工作\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\" aria-label=\"准备工作 permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>准备工作</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>安装CentOS 7.x</li>\n<li>安装Development Tools</li>\n<li>修改内核参数</li>\n<li>安装Java SDK 8</li>\n<li>安装Apache Maven 3</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"安装和配置rabbitmq\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AErabbitmq\" aria-label=\"安装和配置rabbitmq permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装和配置RabbitMQ</h2>\n<h3 id=\"前提条件\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"前提条件 permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>前提条件</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>下载<a href=\"https://github.com/rabbitmq/erlang-rpm/releases/download/v23.0.2/erlang-23.0.2-1.el7.x86_64.rpm\">erlang 23.0.2</a></li>\n<li>下载<a href=\"https://packagecloud.io/rabbitmq/rabbitmq-server/packages/el/7/rabbitmq-server-3.8.5-1.el7.noarch.rpm\">RabbitMQ 3.8.5</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"安装rabbitmq\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85rabbitmq\" aria-label=\"安装rabbitmq permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装RabbitMQ</h3>\n<pre><code>sudo chmod +x erlang-23.0.2-1.el7.x86_64.rpm\nsudo yum -y install erlang-23.0.2-1.el7.x86_64.rpm\nsudo chmod +x rabbitmq-server-3.8.5-1.el7.noarch.rpm\nsudo yum -y install rabbitmq-server-3.8.5-1.el7.noarch.rpm\nsudo service rabbitmq-server start\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"启用管理控制台\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%90%AF%E7%94%A8%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%8F%B0\" aria-label=\"启用管理控制台 permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>启用管理控制台</h3>\n<pre><code>cd /usr/lib/rabbitmq/lib/rabbitmq_server-3.8.5/ebin\nsudo rabbitmq-plugins enable rabbitmq_management\nsudo service rabbitmq-server restart\n</code></pre>\n<p>访问<a href=\"http://localhost:15672\">http://localhost:15672</a>，使用默认用户guest/guest登录。</p>\n<h3 id=\"创建用户\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%88%9B%E5%BB%BA%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7\" aria-label=\"创建用户 permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>创建用户</h3>\n<p>创建cplm用户并设置权限</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rabbitmqctl add_user cplm password\nrabbitmqctl set_user_tags cplm administrator\nrabbitmqctl set_permissions -p '/' 'cplm' '.*' '.*' '.*'\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>注意：将password修改为需要设置的密码。</strong></p>\n<h3 id=\"删除默认用户\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E9%BB%98%E8%AE%A4%E7%94%A8%E6%88%B7\" aria-label=\"删除默认用户 permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>删除默认用户</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">rabbitmqctl delete_user guest\n</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"安装和配置redis\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEredis\" aria-label=\"安装和配置redis permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装和配置Redis</h2>\n<h3 id=\"前提条件-1\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6-1\" aria-label=\"前提条件 1 permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>前提条件</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>下载<a href=\"http://download.redis.io/releases/redis-5.0.8.tar.gz\">Redis 5.0.8</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"安装redis\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85redis\" aria-label=\"安装redis permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装Redis</h3>\n<pre><code>tar xvzf redis-5.0.8.tar.gz\ncd redis-5.0.8\nsudo make install MALLOC=libc\n\nsudo mkdir /etc/redis\nsudo mkdir /var/redis\nsudo mkdir /var/redis/6379\nsudo cp utils/redis_init_script /etc/init.d/redis_6379\nsudo cp redis.conf /etc/redis/6379.conf\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"修改redis配置文件\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9redis%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE%E6%96%87%E4%BB%B6\" aria-label=\"修改redis配置文件 permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>修改Redis配置文件</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>取消绑定本机IP</li>\n<li>设置为守护进程</li>\n<li>启用认证密码</li>\n<li>设置日志文件</li>\n<li>\n<p>设置数据文件夹</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo sed -i 's/^bind 127.0.0.1/# bind 127.0.0.1/g' /etc/redis/6379.conf\nsudo sed -i 's/^daemonize .*/daemonize yes/g' /etc/redis/6379.conf\nsudo sed -i 's/^# requirepass .*/requirepass **password**/g' /etc/redis/6379.conf\nsudo sed -i 's/^logfile .*/logfile \\/var\\/log\\/redis_6379.log/g' /etc/redis/6379.conf\nsudo sed -i 's/^dir .*/dir /var/redis/6379/g' \\/etc\\/redis\\/6379.conf\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>注意：将password修改为需要设置的密码。</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"修改redis启动脚本\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E4%BF%AE%E6%94%B9redis%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8%E8%84%9A%E6%9C%AC\" aria-label=\"修改redis启动脚本 permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>修改Redis启动脚本</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>设置认证密码</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo sed -i 's/$CLIEXEC -p $REDISPORT shutdown/$CLIEXEC -a password -p $REDISPORT shutdown/g' /etc/init.d/redis_6379\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>注意：将password修改为前面步骤设置的密码。</strong></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"启动redis\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%90%AF%E5%8A%A8redis\" aria-label=\"启动redis permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>启动Redis</h3>\n<p>注册为系统服务，并且启动redis服务</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">sudo chkconfig redis_6379 on\nsudo service redis_6379 start\n</code></pre>\n<h3 id=\"检查redis运行状态\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E6%A3%80%E6%9F%A5redis%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%8A%B6%E6%80%81\" aria-label=\"检查redis运行状态 permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>检查Redis运行状态</h3>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">$ redis-cli\n127.0.0.1:6379> auth password\nOK\n127.0.0.1:6379> ping\nPONG\n</code></pre>\n<p><strong>注意：将password修改为前面步骤设置的密码。</strong></p>\n<h2 id=\"安装和配置elasticsearch\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E5%92%8C%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEelasticsearch\" aria-label=\"安装和配置elasticsearch permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>安装和配置ElasticSearch</h2>\n<h3 id=\"前提条件-2\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%E5%89%8D%E6%8F%90%E6%9D%A1%E4%BB%B6-2\" aria-label=\"前提条件 2 permalink\" class=\"post-toc-anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11